Package: MatrixProd
Type: Package
Title: High-Performance Matrix Multiplication
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-07-06
Authors@R: c(
    person("St-Digital-Twin", role = c("cph", "fnd")),
    person("Sergey", "Gumerov", email = "sergey.gumerov@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: High-performance matrix multiplication functions for R, based on extensive
    benchmarking across different implementations. The package includes specialized 
    functions for different matrix sizes, GPU-accelerated functions using OpenCL,
    and CPU-optimized implementations using external libraries. Performance can 
    reach up to 397 GFLOPS on supported hardware.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/St-Digital-Twin/265.MatrixProd
BugReports: https://github.com/St-Digital-Twin/265.MatrixProd/issues
