    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: 
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.6),
    gpuR (>= 2.0.0)
LinkingTo: 
    Rcpp,
    RcppEigen,
    RcppArmadillo
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    bench,
    ggplot2
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Encoding: UTF-8
SystemRequirements: C++17, OpenCL (for GPU acceleration), Apple Accelerate Framework (for Mac)
